# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:448
msgid ""
"The Brightness & Contrast effect allows for the adjustment of the overall "
"lightness or darkness of the image (brightness) and the difference between "
"the darkest and lightest parts of the image (contrast). This effect can be "
"used to correct poorly lit videos or to create dramatic lighting effects for "
"artistic purposes."
msgstr ""
